Weimar Coalition (<span style="color: #c00000;">**SPD**</span> + [? if not lvp_formed: <span style="color: #D3C24D;">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span>?][? if lvp_formed: <span style="color: #FFCC00;">**LVP**</span>?]<span style="color: #000000;"> + **Z**</span>): [+ weimar_coalition_oldenburg +]% 

Grand Coalition (<span style="color: #c00000;">**SPD**</span> + [? if not lvp_formed: <span style="color: #D3C24D;">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: #C0A054;">**DVP**</span>?][? if lvp_formed: <span style="color: #FFCC00;">**LVP**</span>?]<span style="color: #000000;"> + **Z**</span>): [+ grand_coalition_oldenburg +]%

Bourgeois Coalition (<span style="color: #000000;">**Z**</span> + [? if not lvp_formed: <span style="color: #D3C24D;">**[+ ddp_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: #C0A054;">**DVP**</span>?][? if lvp_formed: <span style="color: #FFCC00;">**LVP**</span>?] [? if kvp_formed :+ <span style="color: #0087DC;">**KVP**</span> ?]+ <span style="color: #b8996f;">**WP**</span> + <span style="color: #AFAFAF;">**Others**</span>): [+ true_bourgeois_coalition_oldenburg +]%

Right-Wing Coalition (<span style="color: #3E88B3;">**DNVP**</span> + <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**NSDAP**</span> + <span style="color: #C0A054;">**DVP**</span> + <span style="color: #b8996f;">**WP**</span>[? if cnbl_exists: + <span style="color: #006400;">**CNBL**</span> ?][? if csvd_exists: + <span style="color: #7FCEB1;">**CSVD**</span> ?]): [+ right_coalition_oldenburg +]%

@oldenburg_coalition_menu


- @weimar_coalition_oldenburg
- @grand_coalition_oldenburg
- @bourgeois_coalition_oldenburg
- @left_coalition_oldenburg
- @spd_majority_oldenburg
- @right_wing_coalition_oldenburg
- @nsdap_majority
- @no_coalition_oldenburg

@weimar_coalition_oldenburg
title: A Weimar Coalition will be formed
choose-if: weimar_coalition_oldenburg >= 50 and z_relation >= 65
on-arrival: oldenburg_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; z_relation += 2; ddp_relation += 3; oldenburg_gov = "Weimar"

@grand_coalition_oldenburg
title: A Grand Coalition will be formed
choose-if: grand_coalition_oldenburg > 50 and z_relation >= 60 and dvp_relation >= 67
on-arrival: oldenburg_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; z_relation += 1; dvp_relation += 4; oldenburg_gov = "Grand"

@bourgeois_coalition_oldenburg
title: A bourgeois coalition must be formed
choose-if: true_bourgeois_coalition_oldenburg >= 50
view-if: weimar_coalition_oldenburg < 50 and right_coalition_oldenburg < 50
on-arrival: oldenburg_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; oldenburg_gov = "Bourgeois"

@left_coalition_oldenburg
title: A Coalition of the Left will be formed
subtitle: We will work alongside the KPD
choose-if: left_coalition_oldenburg >= 50 and kpd_relation >= 60
on-arrival: oldenburg_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; unemployed_kpd += 2; new_middle_z -= 1; new_middle_ddp -= 1; new_middle_nsdap += 2; oldenburg_gov = "Left"

@spd_majority_oldenburg
title: SPD majority
subtitle: We don't need any coalition partners
view-if: spd_r_oldenburg >= 50
on-arrival: oldenburg_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; workers_spd += 1; workers_ddp -= 2; rural_spd += 1; new_middle_others -= 1; oldenburg_gov = "SPD"

@right_wing_coalition_oldenburg
title: The DNVP and DVP will work alongside the NSDAP
subtitle: You can't rely on the DVP...
choose-if: right_coalition_oldenburg > 50 and not nsdap_r_oldenburg > 50
view-if: right_coalition_oldenburg >= 50
on-arrival: oldenburg_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; rural_nsdap += 4; oldenburg_gov = "NSDAP"

This can't end well...

@nsdap_majority
title: The NSDAP will govern alone
subtitle: What the...!?!
choose-if: nsdap_r_oldenburg > 50
view-if: nsdap_r_oldenburg >= 50
on-arrival: oldenburg_election_2_trigger_time = time + 48; rural_nsdap += 3; dvp_relation -= 3; oldenburg_gov = "Right"

Why did this have to happen...?

@no_coalition_oldenburg
title: There is no possible government arrangement
subtitle: A caretaker government keeps the buisness running for now.
on-arrival: oldenburg_gov = "Bourgeois"; oldenburg_election_2_trigger_time = time + 25; rural_nsdap += 4; old_middle_nsdap += 1
view-if: (weimar_coalition_oldenburg < 50 and right_coalition_oldenburg < 50) or (z_relation < 60 and dvp_relation < 67 and kpd_relation < 60) or right_coalition_oldenburg < 50
